2.2.1

a. f = f + f + i

add $s0, $s0, $s0 # f = f+f
add $s0, $s0, $s1 # f = f+i

let the value of f and i be stored in $s0 and $s1 respectively

b. f = g + (j + 2)

add  $s0, $s1, $s2  # add g + j, store in f
addi $s0, $s0, 2

