2.2.3 
a. f has the value 6
b. No value for j is defined.  However, if j is supposed to be i with a value of 4, then the value is 8.  (2 + 4 + 2)

2.2.4

a.  add f, f, h
f = f + h

b.  sub f, $0, f
    addi f, f, 1    
Assuming $0 is $zero, f = (-f) + 1

